        "message": "LU-11218 mdd: do not cache atributes on mdd_parent_fid\n\nmdd_is_parent() brings link xattrs of not locked objects into osp\ncache.\nIf that cache become stale a striped directory rename brings an\noutdated link xattr into object xattr table. That makes a directory to\nhave more than one link.\n\nInvalidate osp cache built during mdd_is_subdir().\n\nTest illustrating the issue is added.\n\nSigned-off-by: Vladimir Saveliev <c17830@cray.com>\nCray-bug-id: LUS-6187\nChange-Id: I883854b8d263619594a20c9d37edf33b43508e3f\n"
